data.description: Welcome to 5312 Kaywood Ct! This freshly renovated ranch/rambler sits in a cul de sac and is in a superb location. As you enter the home you are greeted with laminate flooring throughout and stunning vaulted ceilings. The spacious living room comes with a wood burning fireplace and is adjacent to a designated dining area. The peninsula kitchen has freshly painted cabinets, new appliances, plenty of counter top space for all your cooking needs, and a breakfast nook for additional seating. On the upper level is where you will find your hallway bathroom and 3 comfortable bedrooms that all have been freshly painted and have new carpet. The primary suite comes with a walk-in closet and private  bathroom.  The lower level of this home is freshly painted with new light fixtures, giving you an additional living area with open space, powder room, laundry room, and walkout access to your large patio. The patio is perfect for grilling and entertaining, or just sitting and admiring your expansive private  backyard. The exterior of this home also offers you a cozy front porch and plenty of yard space to create your perfect dream garden. Parking is a breeze with your front facing 3 car garage and driveway. Additional features in this home include: HVAC (2022), Water Heater (2022), Garage door openers (2022), Refrigerator (2022), New Stove (2022), Built in microwave (2022), New dishwasher (2023), New carpet (2023), New tile in primary bath (2023), and New light fixtures in hallway + basement (2023). Location is king in real estate, and this home is located in a top rated school district, next to several metro bus stops, the Burke VRE, minutes away from downtown Fairfax, and close proximity to several gorgeous parks, dog parks, and walking trails. This home checks all the boxes! Schedule your home tour today!
